            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>響尾蛇能源(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:FANG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/FANG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">FANG-US</a>)截至台北時間09日01:04股價下跌11.95美元，報183.55美元，跌幅6.11%，成交量2,843,890（股），盤中最高價186.49美元、最低價175.14美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+2.52%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+2.38%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+2.86%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+5.99%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>響尾蛇能源(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:FANG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/FANG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">FANG-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-1.16%</li> <li>近 1 月：+8.29%</li> <li>近 3 月：+39.2%</li> <li>近 6 月：+31.29%</li> <li>今年以來：+30.05%</li></ul></section></main>",
